properties.headline: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS - The Rocks Markets - THE ROCKS George St between Hickson Rd AND Lower Fort St
properties.otherAdvice:
Long term special event clearway parking restrictions will be in effect on George St in The Rocks to accommodate the weekly Rocks Markets.

Clearways will be in effect every weekend from 10pm Friday until 10pm Sunday on the eastern side of George St between Hickson Rd and Lower Fort St.

Clearways are strict no-parking zones and apply even to local residents or Mobility Scheme Permit holders. Check signs before parking as vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.

Road closures will also be in place on weekends for the markets from 4am Saturday until 10pm Sunday on sections on Argyle St, Artherden St, George St, Kendall Lane, Mill Lane and Playfair St.
properties.displayName: SPECIAL EVENT CLEARWAYS - The Rocks Markets

  1. Castlereagh Rd from Jane St to High St: There will be an additional southbound lane.
  2. Mulgoa Rd from High St to Rodley Ave: There will be an additional southbound lane.
  3. Castlereagh Rd from High St to Museum Dr: There will be an additional northbound lane.
  4. High St east of the intersection: There will be an additional westbound right turn lane into Castlereagh Rd.
  5. Castlereagh Rd from Museum Dr to Jane St: There will be an additional southbound lane.
  6. Mulgoa Rd from Rodley Ave to High St: There will be an additional northbound lane.
  7. High St west of the intersection: There will be an additional eastbound lane and right turn lane into Mulgoa Rd.

properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS Northern toll plaza precinct upgrade - MILSONS POINT Sydney Harbour Bridge
properties.otherAdvice:

From 7am Saturday 12 June, the final configuration of the northern toll plaza precinct will open and there will be two general traffic lanes heading south on the Cahill Expy. However, motorists will have to form one lane on approach to the bridge.

One dedicated bus lane will be maintained (lane 7) as well as a bus layover zone.
